# Smart case is the ergonomic default:
#   rg test   -> matches test, Test, TEST
#   rg Test   -> matches Test exactly by case
--smart-case

# Keep giant minified lines readable in terminal output.
--max-columns=150
--max-columns-preview

# Even when using rg -uu, Git internals are almost always noise.
--glob=!.git/*

# Make matches easy to see without changing surrounding text.
--colors=match:fg:yellow
--colors=match:style:bold
